title: South Tower collapses
description: The South Tower of the World Trade Center collapses.

G.W. Bush makes a TV intervention calling the events an "evil, despicable acts of terror".
He sets a goal "to win the war against terrorism".
title: G.W. Bush TV intervention

description: The North Tower collapses (102 minutes after the crash of AA11)
title: North Tower collapses

description: The 47-story Seven World Trade Center collapses. No casualties.
title: Seven WTC collapses

description: Passengers and crew members try to retake the plane. Hijackers deliberately crash the plane, killing all 40 passengers and crew aboard.
title: UA93 crashes in a field

description: Capitol building is evacuated (along with numerous other high-profile buildings, landmarks and public spaces).
title: Capitol evacuation

description: Hijackers crash AA77 into the western aisle of the Pentagon. 59 casualties from the plane and 125 military and civilian killed inside.
title: AA77 crashes on the Pentagon
